        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">The year is established by the relationship between this letter and the <ref target="./DCP-LETT-12677.xml">letter to J. M. F. Ludlow, 4 August 1880</ref>.</note>
             <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD had been advised to consult an actuary on the matter of increasing sickness benefits for members of the Down Friendly Club (see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-12677.xml">letter to J. M. F. Ludlow, 4 August 1880</ref>).</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">The Friendly Club was established in 1850 (see <hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi> vol. 4, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-1293.xml">letter to J. S. Henslow, 17 January [1850]</ref> and n. 6).</note>
